extends layout

block preoutside
  include mixins/nofeedback
  include mixins/socialbuttons
  include includes/fb.jade
  .jumbotron.text-center
    .container
      h1
        img(src='/images/banner.png' alt="Writer's Trail" title="Writer's Trail")
      h2 Now you can keep track of your writings statistics 
        span.fa.fa-signal
      a.btn.btn-lg.btn-primary(href='/signin')
        span.fa.fa-lg.fa-sign-in
        |  Apply for closed beta

  .container
    .text-center
      h1 Sum up all the statistics of your writing
      h3 Sometimes it is not enough to feel that you wrote a lot. Sometimes you need to see it.
      h3 That's what Writer's Trail is here to do.
      h2 Share with your writing buddies!
      +socialbuttons(baseurl, "Writer's Trail", 'Now you can keep track of your writings statistics')
      p
      a(href='/features'): img.full(src='/images/dash.png')

    .feature
      .row
        .col-md-6: .well
          h3
            span.fa.fa-eye
            |  Keep an eye on your progress
          p You can make any amount of projects and each one has its own individual progress bar. Archive them to avoid cluttering the list.
        .col-md-6: .well
          h3
            span.fa.fa-bullseye
            |  Create custom targets
          p 50,000 words in 30 days (as is&x#0020;
            a(href='http://nanowrimo.org' title='NaNoWriMo website') NaNoWriMo
            | )? 100,000 in 45 days? You can choose what you want and even change it midway.
      .row
        .col-md-6: .well
          h3
            span.fa.fa-clock-o
            |  Sessions of any length
          p There's no hard choice of writing sessions length. You can put minutes and seconds, set paused time, mark it as forward and as countdown.
        .col-md-6: .well
          h3
            span.fa.fa-calculator
            |  Writing habits
          p Ever wondered if you are more productive at evening or early morning? The best session length? Now you can know that for sure.
      .row
        .col-md-6: .well
          h3
            span.fa.fa-coffee
            |  Timer and chronometer
          p You can use our watches to keep track of your writing time. Use for your lonely wordsprints late at night (or as you wish).
        .col-md-6: .well
          h3
            span.fa.fa-thumbs-o-up
            |  New features being added
          p We listen to our users and try to make everyone happy. If you provide&#x0020;
            a(href='/feedback') feedback
            | , you may wake up to see the new feature online!
  
    h1.text-center Have a peek at&#x0020;
      a(href='/features' title='Features') Writer's Trail features
      | .
  
  .jumbotron.text-center
    p If you like this tool, consider&#x0020;
      a(href='/donations') donating
      |  to keep it live and free.
    include info/donatebutton.html
    h2 Eyes open for the closed beta test
    a.btn.btn-lg.btn-primary(href='/signin')
        span.fa.fa-lg.fa-sign-in
        |  Apply for it
    p Follow us at 
      a.btn.btn-primary(href='https://facebook.com/writerstrail' title='Facebook')
        span.fa.fa-lg.fa-facebook
      |  and 
      a.btn.btn-info(href='https://twitter.com/writerstrail' title='Twitter')
        span.fa.fa-lg.fa-twitter
      |  to be one of the firsts to try out Writer's Trail.
  .center-block.text-center
    div.fb-like(data-href="https://www.facebook.com/writerstrail" data-layout="standard" data-action="like" data-show-faces="true" data-share="true")
    
  
append styles
  link(rel='stylesheet', href='/stylesheets/home.css')

append scripts
  script(src='/bower_components/RRSSB/js/rrssb.min.js')
